# ============================================================
#  TICKET-SYSTEM — .gitignore
#  Cobre: ASP.NET Core (TicketSystem.API) + React/Vite (TicketSystem.Web)
# ============================================================

# ============================================================
#  🔐 ARQUIVOS SENSÍVEIS — NUNCA SUBIR
# ============================================================
**/appsettings.json
**/appsettings.*.json
!**/appsettings.Example.json

**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

**/secrets.json
**/*secrets*
**/*credentials*

# ============================================================
#  .NET / ASP.NET CORE
# ============================================================

# Build outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/

# Visual Studio
**/.vs/
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.userosscache
**/*.sln.docstates
**/[Dd]ebug/
**/[Rr]elease/

# Pacotes NuGet restaurados (não precisam ir pro repo)
**/packages/
!**/packages/build/
**/*.nupkg
**/*.snupkg
**/project.lock.json
**/project.fragment.lock.json
**/artifacts/

# Logs e diagnóstico
**/[Ll]og/
**/[Ll]ogs/
**/*.log

# Publicação
**/publish/
**/PublishProfiles/

# Testes
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/
**/*.coverage
**/*.coveragexml

# Entity Framework migrations snapshot gerado automaticamente
# (manter as migrations, mas ignorar o snapshot se preferir regenerar)
# **/Migrations/*ModelSnapshot.cs   ← descomente se quiser ignorar

# Rider / JetBrains
**/.idea/

# ============================================================
#  NODE / REACT / VITE (TicketSystem.Web)
# ============================================================

node_modules/
dist/
dist-ssr/
build/
.cache/

# Vite
**/.vite/

# TypeScript
*.tsbuildinfo

# Logs npm/yarn/pnpm
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# Lock files (manter um deles — escolha o do seu gerenciador)
# Descomente a linha do gerenciador que você NÃO usa:
# package-lock.json   ← descomente se usar yarn ou pnpm
# yarn.lock           ← descomente se usar npm
# pnpm-lock.yaml      ← descomente se usar npm

# ============================================================
#  DOCKER
# ============================================================
# Manter o docker-compose.yml mas ignorar overrides locais
docker-compose.override.yml
docker-compose.local.yml
.dockerignore

# ============================================================
#  SISTEMA OPERACIONAL
# ============================================================

# Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# Linux
*~